# Founder pass mint output. manifest.csv holds the PLAINTEXT card codes — the
# only copy outside the printed plastic, since the database stores peppered
# hashes only. The bare `out` entry above already covers this, but that one is
# there for Next's static export: this line is deliberately redundant so that
# removing it can never silently start committing live card codes.
out/manifest.csv
out/*.stl
